  },
  {
    "key": "output|n_nThe_sensations_diffuse_evenly_throughout_your_areolae_incre|0623abe9b24a",
    "original": "\\n\\nThe sensations diffuse evenly throughout your areolae, increasing the amount of tissue to reach your desired shape. <b>Your areolae are now puffy!</b>",
